thread.title: Second day of missing plane search begins as police confirm bag washed ashore is from aircraft
thread.title_full: Second day of missing plane search begins as police confirm bag washed ashore is from aircraft

author: Jane Morice, cleveland.com
title: Second day of missing plane search begins as police confirm bag washed ashore is from aircraft
text: Cleveland police have also confirmed that the contents of a bag found washed ashore Sunday at a beach club in a neighboring suburb belong to a passenger on the missing plane.
